<P>
MAXICARE HEALTH PLANS INC; BUSINESS CLOSINGS; MEDICAL CARE -- SOUTHERN 
CALIFORNIA; MEDICAL CARE -- ORANGE COUNTY; HEALTH MAINTENANCE ORGANIZATIONS; 
FAMILY HEALTH SERVICES INC; CORPORATE RESTRUCTURING 
