</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
PREP ROUNDUP; 
</P>
<P>
JOYNER, CALVERT LEAD ESTANCIA TO GOLF VICTORY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Senior Mike Joyner and junior Ken Calvert shot one-under par 35s to lead 
Estancia High School to a 188-203 victory over Palm Springs in a nonleague 
none-hole golf match Tuesday at Mesa Verde Country Club in Costa Mesa. 
