and coasted the rest of the way. J.J. Cole led Madison (17-14) with 13 points 
and Robby Robinson, and Brad Eaddy added 12 each. Bryon Russell scored 24 
points for San Bernardino, Carlos Dew added 19 and Doug Howard had 11. 
