DODD, CHRISTOPHER J; SENATE (U.S.); POLITICAL APPOINTMENTS; UNITED STATES -- 
GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS; DEPARTMENT OF DEFENSE (U.S.); HEFLIN, HOWELL; VOTING; 
DRINKING; ALCOHOLISM; DOLE, ROBERT J; HOLLINGS, ERNEST F 
