Rushdie, said: "We have therefore decided on security grounds a number of 
Iranians must be required to leave this country. 
</P>
<P>
"We are keeping the activities of other Iranians under very close review," he 
added. He said the expulsion orders would be issued shortly. There are about 
25,000 Iranians in Britain. 
</P>
